# Refund Risk Engine

Rule-based refund risk calculation microservice built with Spring Boot.

## Features

- Rule-based risk calculation (Strategy pattern)
- DTO + Validation
- Global Exception Handling
- Integration and Controller tests
- Clean layered architecture

## Tech Stack

- Java 17
- Spring Boot
- Gradle
- Lombok
- JUnit 5
- MockMvc

## Endpoint

POST /api/risk/calculate

## Architecture

Controller → Validation → Mapper → Service → Risk Rules → Result

## Example Response

{
  "score": 45,
  "level": "MEDIUM"
}
